Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.15,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanna, Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.53,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Wanna come over sometime?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.03,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,To your house?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.28,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Is it fun?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.53,Default,S,0,0,0,,Really fun!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.87,Default,S,0,0,0,,I've got tons of games and snacks.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.29,Default,S,0,0,0,,Plus, we've also got a maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.04,0:00:22.79,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,A maid...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.50,Default,S,0,0,0,,Bring over your maid too.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,Y'know, the one from the dodgeball game{ the other day}.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.54,0:00:32.01,Default,S,0,0,0,,When I told our maid about that, \Nshe said she wanted to meet her.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.47,Default,S,0,0,0,,She wants to talk about the maid life.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.51,Default,S,0,0,0,,You'll come, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.76,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.36,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.61,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Is this where I'll find that reckless fool \Nwho wants to have a maid battle with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.61,0:02:20.87,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I'll destroy her.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring me along?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.87,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Because you know a lot about maids.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.62,Default,S,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome, Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.13,Default,S,0,0,0,,And her maid, and, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.13,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,This is Kobayashi. My guardian.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.88,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Kanna's mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.63,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Do I look that old?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.18,Default,T,0,0,0,,Don't pay it any mind, Miss Kobayshi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.89,Default,T,0,0,0,,Compared to me, all humans are like little babies.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.60,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Milady, I believe introductions are due.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.10,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.10,Default,S,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.61,Default,S,0,0,0,,This is our maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.36,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.40,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,{\move(960,1033,960,1075,2078,2454)}I am Georgie, the maid of this family.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.24,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,So you say you're a maid,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.24,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,but you're not exactly dressed the part.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're not even in black and white.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.25,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,No...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.21,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Maids have never had one fixed uniform.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.21,0:03:15.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,As their role as servants grew more pronounced \Nover their long and storied history,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,their uniforms slowly evolved into what you see today.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.26,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.80,0:03:24.51,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,This is the kind of uniform an apprentice maid \Nwould put together with her allowance.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.39,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Forgive me for not discerning your keen insight sooner.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.89,Default,G,0,0,0,,...the two of us...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.56,Default,Both,0,0,0,,...are kindred spirits!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.90,0:03:37.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,Don't be swayed by some \Nrandom maid, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.65,Default,G,0,0,0,,You must be Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.82,Default,G,0,0,0,,I've heard so much about you \Nfrom the shopping district.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.53,Default,G,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to discuss the maid life with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.91,Default,G,0,0,0,,This way, please!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.42,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,Split,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.75,0:03:56.42,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,Split,Miss Kobayashi's never pulled me along so forcefully before!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.47,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,Okay, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.55,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,Wanna play in my room?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.18,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.98,Default,S,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you want to play?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.27,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.19,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,Oh, this is Twister.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.36,Default,S,0,0,0,Split,The kids' version.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.94,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna play.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.19,Default,S,0,0,0,,Sure, let's give it a go.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.45,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Player one: left hand, yellow.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.95,Default,S,0,0,0,,You play by placing your hands \Nand feet on the colors it tells you to, like so.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.41,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Player two: right hand, blue.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.70,Default,S,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.79,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Player one: left foot, red.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.96,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, th-there, red.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.84,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Player two: right hand, blue.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.46,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Blue.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.26,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Right foot: red.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Red.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.55,Default - Italic,Game,0,0,0,,Left foot: green.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.68,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Green.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.89,Default - Italic,S,0,0,0,,K-Kanna's so soft!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.69,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna play a video game.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.27,Default,S,0,0,0,,I-I've got loads of those.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.69,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Something fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.65,Default,S,0,0,0,,Fun, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Such a nice aroma.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is this first-flush?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.16,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.41,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,I did manage to acquire some \Nfirst-flush Darjeeling.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.25,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,Oh, I know of that.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.87,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,The tasty first plucking, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,Of course I know that much.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, an antique cup!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,From the early Victorian era?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.22,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Yes, I found it at a flea market.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Lady Georgie, what sparked your passion for maids?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,It all started with a picture book.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.64,Default,G,0,0,0,,One where a princess becomes a maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, I've read that book too!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.06,Default,G,0,0,0,,You have? Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,They're professionals who take care of homes!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.78,Default,G,0,0,0,,Their pride in{for} their work \Nhas always made my heart race!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,They change outfits throughout the day!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.70,Default,G,0,0,0,,{\q2}Even during the brief respites from their busy schedules, \Nthey compose themselves with utmost grace!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,Such wonderful demeanor!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.54,Default,S,0,0,0,,How about this game?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.08,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.79,Default,S,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.08,Default,S,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.83,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Sit here.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.67,Default,S,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.17,Default,S,0,0,0,,Like this? There.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.21,Default,S,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.72,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'm most comfortable like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.97,Default,S,0,0,0,,I-I'm in heaven!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.60,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I can't breathe, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.73,Default,S,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! I lost control!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.10,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Hey, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.11,Default,S,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.69,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Am I fitting in with the class?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.32,Default,S,0,0,0,,O-Of course you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.32,0:06:31.12,Default,S,0,0,0,,You can do anything, and everyone praises you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.45,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I feel like something's different.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.75,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I can't explain it very well,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.46,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,but I want something like what \NKobayashi and Lady Tohru have.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.79,Default,S,0,0,0,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.46,Default,S,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry. I love you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.76,Default,S,0,0,0,,I want us to be closer.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.47,Default,S,0,0,0,,Honestly, I love you so much I want to marry you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.05,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.31,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Let's get even closer.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,U-uh, um... I'm not emotionally ready yet...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.02,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Saikawa...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.23,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.78,Default,Georgie,0,0,0,,Join us in extolling the virtue of maids.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.20,Default,T,0,0,0,,Save me, Kanna!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.20,0:07:11.78,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,Apparently, Georgie is Saikawa's older sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,"Georgie" is the nickname she uses \Nwhen she's acting as a maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.55,Default,T,0,0,0,,So she's not a maid, but a maid fanatic?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.30,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.77,Default,Saikawa,0,0,0,,What was Kanna gonna do to me on that pillow?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.10,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure is coming down hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,You decided to live in this world?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.09,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.30,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I've been hanging out with you here a lot recently,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.59,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,so I figured it'd just be easier.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.60,Default,L,0,0,0,,Besides, I found somewhere close by.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.56,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,I'm bunking with a human, same as Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.98,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,What do you say I show you the place?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me. Would they mind?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,Nah. You could help me clear things up too.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,Clear things up?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.74,0:08:37.46,Default,L,0,0,0,,{tried a 1150ms fade-out, but looked weird}Actually, it has to do with why I decided to move to this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.08,0:08:42.87,Default,L,0,0,0,,It happened when I was on my way home \Nfrom your place one night.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.38,Default,L,0,0,0,Joined,Huh? Is someone performing a ritual nearby?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.25,Default,L,0,0,0,,Hmm? A child?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.26,Default,L,0,0,0,,Guess I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.10,0:09:04.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,You let yourself be summoned \Nby a ritual some kid did for fun?{can't think of any less-awkward alternative to passive voice. core of the sentence is "let a ritual summon you," but the "for fun" descriptor makes things messy. perhaps "You let some kid's _____ ritual summon you?" if one were to come up with a good adjective to fill in the blank. but even that's a bit weird.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,Never mind that you agreed to serve him.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.86,Default,L,0,0,0,Joined,Anyway, it turns out they were a family of mages, \Nso they accepted me pretty easily.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,So what exactly do you want to clear up?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,They think I'm a demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.12,Default,L,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you two can set the record straight.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.12,Default,L,0,0,0,,Oh, here we are.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.63,Default,L,0,0,0,,This is Shouta's house.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.54,Default,L,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Can we really?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.51,Default,L,0,0,0,,Nobody's home at this time of day.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.97,Default,L,0,0,0,,They gave me a room upstairs, \Nso we can chill there.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.09,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,That said,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.64,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I've got nothing but tea for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.43,Default,L,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask you something.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,What exactly are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.90,Default,L,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.90,0:09:54.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you were a dragon like Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.15,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I guess I haven't explained.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.78,0:10:02.66,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,If you had to classify me, \Nit'd be as an "ex-god," I guess.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,"Ex"?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.08,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,After a fellow god made her drink cursed booze, she got drunk—
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Right. You mentioned something like that before.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.55,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's how she lost her divinity.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,So what's wrong with "demon"?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.38,0:10:20.18,Default,L,0,0,0,,Well, I'm still responsible \Nfor spreading culture far and wide,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.39,Default,L,0,0,0,,so it's hard to call myself a demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.97,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I'd rather go by{I'd prefer/I prefer} "ex-god,"
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.81,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,"feathered serpent,"
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.27,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,or "Venusian."
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where did "Venusian" come from?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone's home.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.86,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,Must be Shouta, the boy who summoned me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,{\move(960,1033,960,1065,599,1016)}He seems really fidgety.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.49,0:10:44.24,Default,L,0,0,15,,He's always like that when I'm around.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.87,Default,K,0,0,15,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.16,0:10:49.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,Can you really blame him? \NHe's living with an exhibitionist bombshell.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.33,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,That's why, to ease his nervousness a bit,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.96,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I've tried sleeping with him,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.21,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,and taking baths with him,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.97,Default,L,0,0,0,,but nothing seems to work.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.64,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,She brought friends?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.85,Default,L,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Shouta.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,F-Familiars shouldn't act without permission!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.77,Default,L,0,0,0,,Y-You demon!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.40,Default,L,0,0,0,,Are you trying to take over \Nthis house with your friends?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,Looks like he wants to show who's boss.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,Isn't he adorable?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shouta.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.91,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,A-As long as you understand!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.28,0:11:30.87,Default,L,0,0,0,,I invited them over today to help you understand the truth about me.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.13,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.54,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I'm not a demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.38,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,I'm actually a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.01,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,But I used a demon summoning spell.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.01,0:11:45.05,Default,L,0,0,0,Joined,That magic circle could've summoned \Na seriously dangerous and evil demon,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.14,Default,L,0,0,0,,so I decided to beat them to the punch.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.10,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,Split,L-Lies.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.27,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,Split,I don't have enough mana to summon a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.23,0:11:56.82,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Y-You're just bluffing to make yourself seem more powerful!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.53,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,You won't fool me, demon!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.15,Default,L,0,0,0,,So yeah, we end up going \Nfull circle like that every time.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.70,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Shouta.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.45,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.45,0:12:09.87,Default,T,0,0,0,,I hear you're from a family of mages, \Nbut why did you perform a summoning ritual?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.70,0:12:16.04,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,W-Well, I wanted to prove my worth to my parents.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.34,0:12:22.22,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,Split,Right now, as mages, \Nwe're leading quiet lives in this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.84,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,Split,but one day we'll go back home.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.84,0:12:30.56,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,To that end, my dad worked hard \Nto inherit and maintain our bloodline.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.52,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,So I have to hurry up and...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,You summoned Lucoa to show off your power?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.86,0:12:42.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,That actually makes me feel a little bad for her.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.57,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,You make a fair point.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.20,0:12:50.95,Default,K,0,0,0,Joined,Even demons have it hard when \Nthey're summoned for no reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,But it's not like you can take her \Nwith you to grade school,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,so there's no point in her staying here.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.13,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,You're exactly right!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.13,0:12:58.92,Default,L,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.84,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Sorry, Lucoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.01,Default - Italic,L,0,0,0,,Why does it sound like I'm being kicked out?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.59,Default,L,0,0,0,,No, no! It's not like I want to go home!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.55,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.93,0:13:11.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,But you can't just stay here for no reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.43,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,Just look at me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.43,0:13:16.10,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,I'm helping out Miss Kobayashi big time as her maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh? You are?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.19,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,My mom handles all the housework.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.19,0:13:28.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,So, you're saying that if I want to stay here, \NI have to offer you something in return?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.24,Default,L,0,0,0,,How about more gold than you'll ever need?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.25,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm good. My dad can use alchemy.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.25,Default,L,0,0,0,,I can teach you how to farm.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.50,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a farmer.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.63,Default,L,0,0,0,,How about unmatched charisma?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.38,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,I can see the appeal, \Nbut it wouldn't really help me.{assuming this means it would only exacerbate his problems, i.e. Lucoa}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.39,Default,L,0,0,0,,In that case, do you want massive mana reserves?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.14,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,That's certainly an enticing offer.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,We have a deal, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.23,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,But I'm good.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.52,Default,L,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.90,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,I feel like there's no point if you don't earn \Nthat kind of thing for yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.11,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shouta has a good head on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,I don't think Lucoa will ever be of use to him.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.70,Default,L,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.45,Default,L,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.99,Default,L,0,0,0,,All I have left is my body.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.29,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,You really are a demonic succubus!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,You just dug your own grave.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.63,0:14:29.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,Man, seeing Lucoa get all flustered like that was priceless.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.18,Default,T,0,0,0,,Something tells me she's going to stay a succubus for quite a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,By the way, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.14,0:14:35.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.85,0:14:39.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,I discovered something crazy in that house.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.85,0:14:44.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,It seemed like a perfectly normal house to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's about Shouta's father...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,I saw him in a family photo and it hit me.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he's my company's managing director.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.20,Default,T,0,0,0,,Small world, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.21,Default,L,0,0,0,,Shouta!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.62,Default,S,0,0,0,,Whoa! Don't come in!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.84,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,Look, I'm not a demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.88,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,Take a closer look!{ಠ_ಠ}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.26,Default - Top,Shouta,0,0,0,,Begone, accursed demon!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.84,Default,L,0,0,0,,Come on, don't look the other way!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.84,Default - Top,Shouta,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.56,Default,T,0,0,0,,It just won't let up.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.48,Default,T,0,0,0,,I guess it {\i1}is{\i0} the rainy season.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Let's hang these up.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.40,Default,T,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair-weather dolls.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.86,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Fair-weather dolls?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.28,Default,T,0,0,0,,Will those things really make the rain let up?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,Eventually.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.67,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Okay, Kobayashi. I'm out.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Guess I should head home too.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,No overtime today, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.40,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm really glad you came home early.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,I come home as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,Takiya left on time too.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,Takiya...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,I wonder if Takiya and Fafnir \Nare doing okay as roommates.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \NI haven't seen Fafnir lately.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.04,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I saw him today.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,You did? Where?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.96,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,At the playground, on the way home from school.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.79,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,He was jumping in circles over and over
Dialogue: 100,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.34,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,and mumbling to himself.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,What is that curse dragon{again, a dragon that deals in curses} up to?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.05,0:16:36.93,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Kings!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.68,Default,F,0,0,0,,Rule.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.43,Default,Taki,0,0,0,,Subjects!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.18,Default,F,0,0,0,,Suck.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,Nyami-nyami!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.06,Default,F,0,0,0,,Reigns supreme.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.68,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Kaboom!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.06,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,Nice!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.69,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,Looking very nice!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.07,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,You've improved really quickly, Faf.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.74,Default,F,0,0,0,,Who's Faf?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.03,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Oh, did I offend you?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.82,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,My apologies, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.00,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Now we've got the calls and responses down pat for tomorrow's event.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.29,Default,F,0,0,0,,We can get our hands on limited edition merch at that event, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.71,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.42,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Tonight's dinner is curry.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.80,Default,F,0,0,0,,Mild?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.01,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.47,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.47,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.18,Default,F,0,0,0,,I won't lose today.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.52,Default,F,0,0,0,,Damn it, a trap?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.31,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,What did you just hide?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.31,Default,F,0,0,0,,You fool. You can't go that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.90,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Weapon acquired!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.28,Default,Fafnir,0,0,0,,I got knocked out.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.49,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Victory is mine, it seems.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.78,Default,F,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.37,Default,F,0,0,0,,I won't lose next time.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.20,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have it any other way.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.21,0:17:52.50,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Sir Fafnir, could you give this game a test run for me?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.46,Default,F,0,0,0,,You mean the one you're selling at Comiket?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.92,0:17:59.05,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Indeed. I'm at about the 80% mark, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.47,Default,F,0,0,0,,Which part?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.22,Default,Taki,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.57,Default,F,0,0,0,,Can't you improve this somehow?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.90,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,That really is the problem area, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.91,0:18:25.04,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Sir Fafnir, about how many hours do you spend logged in a day?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.41,Default,F,0,0,0,,Around 21 or so.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.37,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,What's your level now?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.92,Default,F,0,0,0,,280.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.92,Default,F,0,0,0,,I've cleared all the limited-time events, \Nso I'm bored now.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.72,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,You've totally become a hopeless MMO addict.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.99,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Sir Fafnir.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.11,Default,F,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.95,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I bought you some conditioner \Non the way home from work today.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.37,Default,F,0,0,0,,Will this help my hair?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.70,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.13,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.05,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,I'm conking out.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.76,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,Good night, Sir Fafnir.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.73,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sir Fafnir.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.65,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Breakfast this morning is rice and natto.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.07,Default,F,0,0,0,,Mild?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.15,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Negatory.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.70,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Rain, rain, rain...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna must really like her new umbrella.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.91,0:19:51.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,Don't you know what they say?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,Sharing an umbrella signifies a deep bond.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:00.47,0:20:04.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know that, but you have your own.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,I like it better this way.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,Looks like they're getting along just fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.08,Default,T,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be saying this as the one \Nwho suggested it, but Takiya's incredible.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not just anyone can live with Fafnir.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.96,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Humans can be one of two things: winners or busts.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.17,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,You can identify the busts almost immediately,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.97,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,but only time can tell whether you've truly found a winner.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.22,0:20:46.60,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1350)}I can't be bothered to waste \Nthat much time on mere humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.64,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,As far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.64,0:20:53.23,Default - Italic,Fafnir,0,0,0,,humans might as well all be busts who encroach \Non my home to steal what is rightfully mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.48,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.81,Default - Italic,F,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.44,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Can't wait for the event, huh, Faf—
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.98,0:21:01.90,Default,F,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.86,Default,F,0,0,0,,You're a winner.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.66,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Faf...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:05.91,0:21:06.91,Default,F,0,0,0,,Let us make haste.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.49,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.34,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,The fair-weather dolls aren't working at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,It sure is raining cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.56,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I like the rain.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.07,Default,K,0,0,0,,You might have a point.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,The rain's not so bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:26.34,0:23:29.01,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,Lucoa, no more approaching me naked!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:29.01,0:23:30.30,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.30,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,Split,But my clothes are just my scales,
Dialogue: 100,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.85,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,Split,so technically I'm always naked.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.85,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,,G-Get away from me, pervert!
