Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.96,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.21,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}with no choice but to sing along
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.21,0:01:17.55,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}That's just how it is at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.55,0:01:21.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}feeling like you're not in control
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.77,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}But if you open up and listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(180,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}(Anywhere is fine!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.65,0:01:38.53,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,160)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I have the courage to become your wings
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.08,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I'll take on the world without any fear
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.08,0:01:46.00,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(220,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}as long as I feel this magic
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.79,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.79,0:01:56.67,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(170,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}wrapped up together in this moment
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.34,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}We communicate on different levels,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.64,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,240)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
