Comment: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.45,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Tell me, how did I get here?
Comment: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.41,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Comment: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:05.12,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Comment: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Why now of all times
Comment: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.96,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.21,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:17.55,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:21.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.77,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:38.53,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.08,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:46.00,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.79,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:56.67,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.34,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.64,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
