Comment: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.27,ED-E,clipin,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Come on, snuggle with me
Comment: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:26.36,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Get over here and quit being a tease!
Comment: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.82,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HEBAFE9&}Why must the rules be so strict?
Comment: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:31.03,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}It's like my heart's bound in chains
Comment: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:35.49,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,What an inferior and foolish system of values
Comment: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:37.70,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}It just isn't any good
Comment: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.66,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}These "morals" of yours are worthless
Comment: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:43.50,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}Ah~ I wanna eradicate it all!
Comment: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:49.05,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let's do some interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:53.30,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,and eclipse the world with our passion
Comment: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.93,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,A whole week of that?
Comment: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:02.52,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,It'd be more precious than an eternity
Comment: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:05.94,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,The past and the future don't mean a thing
Comment: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.06,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Simply being here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.32,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,with the people here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.28,ED-E,nooffset,0,0,0,karaoke,is what I love!
Comment: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.66,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.04,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,supersimple imagination
Comment: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:25.00,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Eliminate common sense and you're in paradise! Paradise!
